<!-- Per MOS:BOLDTITLE and WP:SBE, neither the article's title nor related text appears in bold.-->'''2017年莫科阿土石流'''發生於當地時間2017年4月1日凌晨，位於[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]][[普图马约省|普图马约省]][[莫科阿|莫科阿]]的暴洪及山崩，當日的強降雨為發生原因，造成至少311人死亡，超過400人受傷，另有178人失蹤。此次事件的罹難人數居哥倫比亞史上天氣相關災難第三位<ref name="Wunderground">{{cite web|author=Jeff Masters|publisher=Weather Underground|date=3 April 2017|accessdate=4 April 2017|title=Meteorology of Saturday's Colombian Flood Disaster That Killed 254|url=https://www.wunderground.com/cat6/meteorology-saturdays-colombian-flood-disaster-killed-254?mr=1|archive-date=2018-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209124100/https://www.wunderground.com/cat6/meteorology-saturdays-colombian-flood-disaster-killed-254?mr=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦為莫科阿史上最嚴重的災害<ref>{{cite news|author=Justicia|newspaper=El Tiempo|date=2 April 2017|accessdate=2 April 2017|title=La avalancha que provocó la peor catástrofe en la historia de Mocoa|url=http://www.eltiempo.com/colombia/otras-ciudades/avalancha-en-mocoa-cifras-de-la-tragedia-y-causas-73984|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330020359/https://www.eltiempo.com/colombia/otras-ciudades/avalancha-en-mocoa-cifras-de-la-tragedia-y-causas-73984|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/4726569/mocoa-colombia-flooding-disaster/|title=Years of Warnings, But No Action Proceeded Deadly Floods in Colombia|publisher=Time|date=5 April 2017|author=Ben Fox and Alba Tobella|accessdate=2017-04-08|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409233605/http://time.com/4726569/mocoa-colombia-flooding-disaster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

